            <scopecontent id="aspace_bb0ec92abfedcb37150f2429bd730882">
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>Includes small papers with Chinese characters printed on them for use in language learning. Some papers have handwritten English translations and pronunciations on the back and some have printed color images. This folder also includes some ephemera that was stored with the language flash cards including several of Viney's business cards.</p>
